[26/02/2018 19:28:53] <font color="#00ffff">He venido a conocer al granjero</font>
[26/02/2018 19:28:53] <font color="#00ffff">y experto en cebollas,</font>
[26/02/2018 19:28:54] <font color="#00ffff">Alastair Findlay.</font>
[26/02/2018 19:28:56] <font color="#00ffff">Alastair, soy Matt.</font>
[26/02/2018 19:28:56] <font color="#ffffff">Encantado de conocerte.</font>
[26/02/2018 19:28:58] <font color="#00ffff">Lo mismo digo.</font>
[26/02/2018 19:28:58] <font color="#ffffff">Sí.</font>
[26/02/2018 19:29:00] <font color="#00ffff">¿Son tus cebollas? Mira eso.</font>
